                    "description": "For 25 years I worked mainly with the international office of the Vrije Universiteit in teacher education projects abroad. From 1981 - 1991 I was based in Indonesia where I assisted Satya Wacana Christian University in Salatiga with the development and teaching of newly established science and mathematics teacher education programs and with outreach in-service programs. From 1996 - 2002 I did the same at the University of San Carlos in Cebu City, Philippines. From 1991-1996 I taught physics education in the teacher education program at VU, supervised research, and acted as a consultant to science education projects  including for the World Bank. From 2002 - 2004 I was consultant to science education projects abroad andwas part-time on loan to projects at the Universities of Utrecht (Modern Physics) and Amsterdam (elementary science and technology).",
